416
00:28:12,480 --> 00:28:13,480
What type?

417
00:28:14,440 --> 00:28:16,800
That guy is from our sports school.

418
00:28:17,400 --> 00:28:18,320
I think

419
00:28:18,600 --> 00:28:21,280
