of a crush on Liu Danyang.

420
00:28:21,480 --> 00:28:23,560
They climbed mountains together before.

421
00:28:24,240 --> 00:28:25,160
Liu Danyang asked him,

422
00:28:25,800 --> 00:28:26,640
"Do you believe

423
00:28:26,650 --> 00:28:28,160
