437
00:28:52,560 --> 00:28:53,480
What are you laughing at?

438
00:28:54,880 --> 00:28:55,800
Nothing.

439
00:28:56,000 --> 00:28:57,080
I told them

440
00:28:57,520 --> 00:28:58,640
mountain climbing is your thing.

441
00:28:59,440 --> 00:29:00,440
Of course.

442
00:29:01,880 --> 00:29:03,280
Back in sports school,

443
00:29:03,640 --> 00:29:05,680
