444
00:29:06,480 --> 00:29:07,400
but I

445
00:29:07,920 --> 00:29:09,080
could do it in just one hour.

446
00:29:10,880 --> 00:29:12,960
That's why you're called
the "Mountain pro".

447
00:29:13,160 --> 00:29:14,280
I'll learn from you.

