483
00:31:49,710 --> 00:31:50,960
No, you...

484
00:32:09,840 --> 00:32:10,760
Have you eaten?

485
00:32:19,160 --> 00:32:20,160
That can fill your stomach?

486
00:32:20,160 --> 00:32:22,040
